show.description:
Dard, dhokha aur taqdeer ke panjon mein jakkad chuke, Yung Chang aur Sophie ki kahani ek khatarnak mod par pahunch jaati hai. Jab Yung Chang apni pyaari Sophie ko har jagah dhoondhne ki koshish karta hai, tab Sophie apni zindagi ki sabse badi takleefon aur dard se guzarti hai. Ek shocking twist mein, woh apni yaadein kho deti hai… Aur uska poora past ek dhundh ban jaata hai. Phir bhi, taqdeer ne in dono ke liye kuch aur hi socha hota hai. Woh phir milte hain… lekin apne apne dard aur faislon ke saath kabhi ek nahi ho paate. Yeh kahani hai — pyaar, dhokhe, dard aur qurbaaniyon ki,
jahan taqdeer apna sabse kathor khel khelti hai.
